        $arg1 = $_POST['arg1'];
        $arg2 = $_POST['arg2'];
        $arg2 = $_POST['arg3'];
        $admin = new Ad($cmd, $clazz, $func1, $func2, $func3, $arg1, $arg2, $arg3);
        $admin->check();
    }
}
else {
    echo "You r not admin!";
}
```

[关于PHP反射类](https://www.jianshu.com/p/d02cbde1cdd7)

